302
00:16:52,654 --> 00:16:56,830
I'm the me from a future that's a little
further down form the me you know right now.

303
00:16:57,124 --> 00:16:58,497
I wanted to see you.

304
00:17:00,383 --> 00:17:02,073
Hey! You don't trust me?!

305
00:17:02,541 --> 00:17:04,090
Okay, this'll prove it.

306
00:17:04,178 --> 00:17:07,436
See, I've got it a tiny star-shaped mole right here.

307
00:17:07,516 --> 00:17:09,129
It's not a fake mole, either.

308
00:17:09,208 --> 00:17:10,074
Wanna touch it?

309
00:17:10,099 --> 00:17:10,796
Super-size me!

310
00:17:10,821 --> 00:17:12,036
You believe me now?

311
00:17:12,490 --> 00:17:16,263
Whether I believe her or not, I don't
recall where Miss Asahina keeps her moles.

312
00:17:16,414 --> 00:17:20,377
<i>The only time I was able to see that much of her
body was when she was cosplaying as a bunny girl.</i>

313
00:17:20,512 --> 00:17:22,564
<i>And that other time when I peeked in as she changed...</i>

314
00:17:22,589 --> 00:17:24,078
<i>Which wasn't my fault!</i>

315
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:28,143
<i>I never saw any moles because I never
made it a point to go looking for them.</i>

316
00:17:28,682 --> 00:17:32,757
Oh? Well, I remember that you were the
one who told me that I had a mole here.

317
00:17:32,908 --> 00:17:35,283
I didn't even know I had one there until you...

318
00:17:36,902 --> 00:17:39,559
I... just... Oh no!

319
00:17:39,906 --> 00:17:41,059
This is before we...

320
00:17:41,424 --> 00:17:44,831
Oh, what have I done?! I totally screwed up just now.

321
00:17:44,856 --> 00:17:47,953
I'm sorry, Kyon, just forget everything I said, okay?

322
00:17:47,978 --> 00:17:49,327
<i>Easy for you to say.</i>

323
00:17:49,981 --> 00:17:52,360
It's all right, really. I believe you, I do.

324
00:17:52,754 --> 00:17:57,473
The truth is, with everything that's going on, I'm in the
right frame of mind to believe just about anything today.

325
00:17:57,623 --> 00:18:02,066
Wait, if you're standing here, that means there's
two Miss Asahinas in the same time plane, right?

326
00:18:02,772 --> 00:18:04,433
Ah. Right.

327
00:18:04,742 --> 00:18:07,994
The past, I mean, the me from the past, the younger me,

328
00:18:08,381 --> 00:18:11,908
right now, she's eating lunch in my
old classroom with all her classmates.

329
00:18:11,948 --> 00:18:14,203
There's something important I had to tell you,

330
00:18:14,228 --> 00:18:18,246
so I pulled some strings and they finally
let me come back to this time plane again.

331
00:18:18,271 --> 00:18:21,593
If you're wondering, I asked
Miss Nagato to step out for a bit.

332
00:18:21,618 --> 00:18:24,025
Wait, Miss Asahina, you know about Nagato?

333
00:18:24,286 --> 00:18:26,392
Sorry, that's classified.

334
00:18:27,394 --> 00:18:30,094
Wow, it's been forever since I last said that.

335
00:18:30,119 --> 00:18:32,356
Funny, I heard you say it a couple days ago.

336
00:18:32,381 --> 00:18:32,992
Ah...

337
00:18:36,317 --> 00:18:40,584
I won't be able to stay here much
longer, so listen, cause this is important.

338
00:18:40,980 --> 00:18:43,107
Do you know the story of Snow White?

339
00:18:44,048 --> 00:18:45,453
Uh, yeah, sure I do.

340
00:18:45,478 --> 00:18:48,431
From now on, if you ever find yourself in danger,

341
00:18:48,590 --> 00:18:50,483
I want you to remember those words.

342
00:18:50,618 --> 00:18:51,532
