danger, I just had some of that yesterday.

346
00:19:02,025 --> 00:19:04,953
That's not the one I'm talking about. It's worse.

347
00:19:05,363 --> 00:19:07,999
Let's see... I can't give you any details,

348
00:19:08,024 --> 00:19:11,121
but when the time comes, Miss
Suzumiya should be at your side.

349
00:19:11,146 --> 00:19:13,085
Huh? You mean me and Haruhi?

350
00:19:13,227 --> 00:19:14,214
What's gonna happen?

351
00:19:14,975 --> 00:19:19,986
When it does happen, Miss Suzumiya probably
won't consider the event to be all that dangerous.

352
00:19:20,524 --> 00:19:25,250
But it will be. And not just for you and her,
but for all of us, so just keep that in mind.

353
00:19:25,369 --> 00:19:27,832
Oh, come on, can't you give me any more details?

354
00:19:27,943 --> 00:19:29,303
Is that classified, too?

355
00:19:29,756 --> 00:19:35,498
I am sorry, but I thought that if I at least
gave you a hint... This is the best I can do...

356
00:19:36,001 --> 00:19:38,153
So that's why you're telling me about Snow White?

357
00:19:38,542 --> 00:19:39,376
Yeah...

358
00:19:40,106 --> 00:19:41,679
Okay, I'll try to remember.

359
00:19:48,592 --> 00:19:51,175
I'm amazed I could wear something like this.

360
00:19:51,263 --> 00:19:53,042
It's out of the question now.

361
00:19:53,178 --> 00:19:56,536
Well then, can you tell me what other
