362
00:19:57,031 --> 00:19:59,994
That's a secret. It's just too embarrassing.

363
00:20:00,248 --> 00:20:02,599
Besides, you'll find out soon enough.

364
00:20:03,154 --> 00:20:05,001
Well, I better go...

365
00:20:10,006 --> 00:20:11,784
Something else I need to tell you...

366
00:20:12,523 --> 00:20:15,438
Don't get too friendly with me, okay...?

367
00:20:16,262 --> 00:20:17,812
Wait, I just wanna know something!

368
00:20:19,055 --> 00:20:22,225
Miss Asahina, how old are you right now?

369
00:20:23,744 --> 00:20:25,245
That's classified.

370
00:20:26,046 --> 00:20:29,469
<i>That was a smile that would make
anyone who saw it fall in love.</i>

371
00:20:33,729 --> 00:20:35,036
It's been ages.

372
00:20:35,061 --> 00:20:39,679
<i>In other words, the high school version of Miss
Asahina is gonna return to her time in the future.</i>

373
00:20:39,949 --> 00:20:41,536
<i>I wonder when that's gonna happen...?</i>

374
00:20:42,057 --> 00:20:45,489
<i>And how many years between the one that's
