377
00:20:53,702 --> 00:20:55,162
<i>Better get back to the classroom.</i>

378
00:20:55,950 --> 00:20:57,540
<i>Man, I'm really hungry.</i>

379
00:20:58,796 --> 00:21:03,411
Hey, you didn't happen to pass someone in the hall
just now that looked a lot like Miss Asahina, did you?

380
00:21:03,782 --> 00:21:06,507
The Mikuru Asahina from another time plane,

381
00:21:06,532 --> 00:21:07,789
I met her this morning.

