00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:26,458
It is so.

390
00:21:26,743 --> 00:21:28,015
Then I guess it's my loss.

391
00:21:28,285 --> 00:21:29,222
Your loss.

392
00:21:29,906 --> 00:21:32,424
Nagato, thanks again for yesterday.

